{"tid":679282,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[見證王者之戰]17-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃決賽--新垣結衣 對 IU","createTime":"2018-05-26T17:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T03:36:15.000Z","uid":92376,"like":172,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"61efa7cd5fb8dc04a8c4fc1e68ccea23ab611aaf","tid":679282,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:30:00.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可直接以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣 v IU<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃決賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-5-27 1:30am-11:30pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HIUU4il.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHIUU4il.png&h=1decc683&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Y6Bfi0S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FY6Bfi0S.png&h=7c2b2042&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fDKJUOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfDKJUOh.png&h=cf9c1fd7&s={SIZE}\" />新垣結衣 v IU<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sbXOEPJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsbXOEPJ.png&h=db4323d3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃決賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">決賽不設額外分數。若賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"64d8d9fa0b654e50d0eb3977d242aa288e82ff00","tid":679282,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:31:39.